.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B LD_LIBRARY_PATH
Must include the directory containing
.I librtlsdr.so.0
(built by cargo in
.IR target/*/build/*/out/rtlsdr-build/src ).
The wrapper script
.B dabctl.sh
sets this automatically.
.TP
.B RUST_LOG
Controls log verbosity (e.g.,
.BR debug ", " info ", " warn ).
The default level is
.BR info .
.SH FILES
.TP
.I dabctl.sh
Shell wrapper that sets
.B LD_LIBRARY_PATH
and runs
.BR dabctl .
.TP
.I live\-capture\-iq2pcm.sh
Live capture script: decodes audio and saves WAV, JSON metadata, and slideshow images.
.SH HARDWARE
Requires an RTL-SDR dongle (RTL2832U chipset with R820T/R820T2 tuner)
and a DAB antenna for Band III reception (174\-240 MHz).
.PP
The
.B dvb_usb_rtl28xxu
kernel module must be blacklisted:
.RS
.nf
echo "blacklist dvb_usb_rtl28xxu" | sudo tee /etc/modprobe.d/rtlsdr.conf
sudo rmmod dvb_usb_rtl28xxu
.fi
.RE
